data.title: HAVEN of Oakland County MI
data.text:
The Story of HAVEN

HAVEN seeks to eliminate domestic violence and sexual assault across Oakland County and the surrounding communities by empowering survivors through advocacy and social change. Learn more about HAVEN's mission

HAVEN Success Stories

HAVEN has helped domestic violence and sexual assault victims and their families escape abuse and create safer lives for over 40 years. Our survivor-centered services honor survivors as experts of their own experiences. Read HAVEN success stories

What you can do to help

HAVEN relies on the generosity of the community to help victims of domestic and sexual violence on their road to recovery. Volunteer your time Donate items or make a financial gift
